reviewText: Could not be used in US DVD players.  Was for United Kingdom.
I like it!  The condition of the DVD is very good. The pictures and sound are excellent! Thank you very much!

This was a treat.  We went to Versailles and were overwhelmed with its beauty.  This dvd was a wonderful souvenir of the visit and we saw a lot in the dvd that we had missed when in France.  So glad to have this in my library!
